5.1  Surface
	•	Tabs at top: All / Strength / Conditioning / Mobility / Skill.
	•	Filter chips below: Equipment (Barbell / DB / KB / Bodyweight / Machine / Bands), Muscle group, Movement pattern (Squat / Hinge / Push / Pull / Carry / Locomotion / Rotation).
